(51, 8, '<section style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: center; line-height: 2em;">\r\n	<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">九月重阳日，东篱菊也黄。</strong></section>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); clear: both; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: center; line-height: 2em;">\r\n	<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">俗人多泛酒，谁解助茶香。</strong></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: center;">\r\n	<img alt="重阳节海报.jpg" src="/qxcy/uploads/allimg/211027/151552J91-0.jpg" style="border: 0px;height: auto;display: block;" title="重阳节海报.jpg" /></p>\r\n', '', '', '171.37.178.31'),
(52, 8, '<div>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: center;">\r\n		<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">凝玉花上露，清影入晚秋。</strong></p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: center;">\r\n		<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">捧一杯茶，伴秋凉。</strong></p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; text-align: center;">\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; text-align: center;">\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px 0px;">\r\n		<img alt="寒露海报.jpg" src="/qxcy/uploads/allimg/211027/151T23349-0.jpg" style="border: 0px;  height: auto; display: block; text-align: center;" title="寒露海报.jpg" /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="pages" style="margin: 0px; padding: 40px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: SiYuanheiti, Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">\r\n	<ul style="margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style: none;">\r\n	</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n', '', '', '171.37.178.31'),
(53, 3, '<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	<a href="https://www.chaliyi.com/enshiyulu/" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: blue; user-select: text !important;" target="_blank">恩施玉露</a>的功效与与作用主要是能抗氧化，提高免疫力等。同时它可以清除体内垃圾，减轻心脑血管负担,通过防止器官老化、有效分解和清除体内垃圾;延缓器官衰老，使中老年人心脑血管年轻化。</p>\r\n<p align="center" style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	<img alt="恩施玉露的作用与功效" src="/qxcy/uploads/allimg/211027/15493C516-0.jpg" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px 15px; border: 0px; max-width: 790px; user-select: text !important;" /></p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	恩施玉露的功效与与作用：</p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	1、解毒排毒，健康清道夫，硒之所以被称为体内垃圾，在于它能够充分调动人体内在能量，通过加强人体免疫力，启动人体保健系统，更加充分有效地清除体内垃圾，解毒排毒。</p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	2、天然解毒剂，硒能大幅度降低、解除环环境中有害因素诱发的臻畸、致癌毒性。硒对体外辐射有保护作用，所经经常接触电视、手机、电脑等各种辐干扰的人补硒。</p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	3、胰腺卫士，补硒可有效恢复胰腺功能。</p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	4、补硒可以保护胰腺不受伤害，补硒后血清和胰腺的淀粉酶、脂肪酶的活性都能明显提高，特别是同时补硒和VE的提高幅度最大。补硒可保护胰腺，进而保护营养物质的消化吸收和消化道的正常生理机能。</p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	5、补硒可以促进胰岛B细胞的分泌功能，胰腺的无管腺属于内分泌系统，腺体细胞象岛一样游离在有管腺腺泡的间隙中，称为胰岛。专家发现，缺少硒对胰岛的伤害很大，缺硒直接减少胰岛素等多肽类激素的合成与分泌，引起血清中胰岛素、C肽水平显著下降。</p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	恩施玉露茶的饮用方法：</p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	恩施玉露冲泡水温在80&deg;左右，用煮沸过的水少许冲入茶杯以湿润<a href="https://www.chaliyi.com/" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: blue; user-select: text !important;" target="_blank">茶叶</a>，吸水后开始慢慢膨胀的茶芽，有如春笋破土，杨柳吐绿，润物细无声。</p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	冲泡恩施玉露，用茶壶冲泡时，先用回转冲泡法向内回旋3周冲入开水，此手法有向客人招手、表示欢迎之意。再用直流冲水法冲至八成满，最后用&ldquo;凤凰三点头&rdquo;的手势冲至壶满，刮去表面浮沫，加盖，静置2&mdash;3分钟。然后，将品茶杯排好，来回倒茶，使每杯茶汤浓度均匀</p>\r\n', '', '', '0.0.0.0'),
(54, 3, '<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	自古文人墨客对茶文化从不吝赞，而备受人称道的当属<strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); user-select: text !important;"><a href="https://www.chaliyi.com/xihulongjin/" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: blue; user-select: text !important;" target="_blank">西湖龙井</a>茶</strong>。&ldquo;西湖之泉，以虎跑为最，两山之茶以龙井为佳&rdquo;，龙井茶，诗词，文人，三者紧密相连。而如今，西湖龙井有了新的定位，健康养生。喝西湖龙井茶不仅是心灵享受，还能健康养生。下面就来看看喝西湖龙井茶有哪些好处?</p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	　　1、西湖龙井茶非常适合一些肥胖的人喝，因为其当中含有咖啡碱以及叶酸等成分，可以有效地帮助分解体内的脂肪组织，进而起到减肥的效果。</p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	　　2、西湖龙井茶对于一些有肾功能缺陷的患者来说也是非常适合的，因为其当中所富含的茶碱是可以强效地帮助利尿，对于治理肾功能疾病是很有帮助的。</p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	　　3、口腔溃疡患者是因为没有注意口腔内的卫生等，这时可以通过用西湖龙井茶来漱口之后再喝，会对治疗溃疡有很大的效果，因为西湖龙井茶当中的茶多酚以及鞣酸是可以有效帮助消毒杀菌的。</p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; text-align: center; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	<img alt="西湖龙井茶" src="/qxcy/uploads/allimg/211027/1553145303-0.jpg" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px 15px; border: 0px; max-width: 790px; user-select: text !important;" /></p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	　　4、对于一些高血压患者来说，喝西湖龙井茶，就等于是在吃降压药，西湖龙井茶当中所具有的维C以及茶多酚，是可以帮助软化动脉，并且活血化瘀，可以让高血压的发病率大大减少。</p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	　　5、西湖龙井茶具有一种舒缓支气管痉挛的茶碱成分，可以有效促进血液的循环，对于一些中老年人来说是非常适合喝的一种茶，因为老年人的气管会更加敏感一些。</p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	　　有人说诗情画意之余不能兼得健康养生。然而西湖龙井茶就做到了，午后阳光，一本书，一杯茶，当淡淡的茶香融进浓浓的墨香，这不就是你要的身心舒畅吗?</p>\r\n', '', '', '0.0.0.0'),
(55, 3, '<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	碧螺春作为<a href="https://www.chaliyi.com/lvcha/" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: blue; user-select: text !important;" target="_blank">绿茶</a>代表之一的碧螺春，风格独具，驰名中外，其功效也常被人们津津乐道。碧螺春<a href="https://www.chaliyi.com/" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: blue; user-select: text !important;" target="_blank">茶叶</a>成分对人体的生理、药理功效是多种多样的，<a href="https://www.chaliyi.com/article/19095.html" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: blue; user-select: text !important;" target="_blank">碧螺春的功效</a>与作用有抗癌症，抗衰老，抗心脑血管疾病，提神，减肥，解酒，防辐射，防龋齿和利尿的功效和作用，下面详细介绍碧螺春的功效与作用和禁忌。</p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; text-align: center; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	<img alt="碧螺春的功效与作用" src="/qxcy/uploads/allimg/211027/1555212630-0.jpg" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px 15px; border: 0px; max-width: 790px; user-select: text !important;" /></p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	<strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); user-select: text !important;">一、碧螺春的功效与作用:</strong></p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	<strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); user-select: text !important;">1、兴奋作用</strong></p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;碧螺春茶叶的咖啡因能兴奋中枢神经系统，帮助人们振奋精神、增进思维、消除疲劳、提高效率。</p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	<strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); user-select: text !important;">2、利尿作用</strong></p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;碧螺春茶叶中的咖啡因和茶碱具有利尿作用，用于治疗水肿、尿潴留。利用<a href="https://www.chaliyi.com/hongcha/" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: blue; user-select: text !important;" target="_blank">红茶</a>糖水的解毒、利尿作用能治疗急性黄疸型肝炎。</p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	<strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); user-select: text !important;">3、强心解痉作用</strong></p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;碧螺春茶叶中咖啡因具有强心、解痉、松弛平滑肌的功效，能解除支气管痉挛，促进血液循环，是治疗支气管哮喘、止咳化痰、心肌梗死的良好辅助药物。</p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	<strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); user-select: text !important;">4、抑制动脉硬化作用</strong></p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;碧螺春茶叶中的茶多酚和维生素c都有活血化瘀防止动脉硬化的作用。所以经常饮茶的人当中，高血压和冠心病的发病率较低。</p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	<strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); user-select: text !important;">5、抗菌、抑菌作用</strong></p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;碧螺春茶中的茶多酚和鞣酸作用于细菌，能凝固细菌的蛋白质将细菌杀死。可用于治疗肠道疾病，如霍乱、伤寒、痢疾、肠炎等。皮肤生疮、溃烂流脓外伤破了皮，用浓茶冲洗患处，有消炎杀菌作用。口腔发炎、溃烂、咽喉肿痛，用茶叶来治疗，也有一定疗效。</p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	<strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); user-select: text !important;">6、减肥作用</strong></p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;碧螺春茶中的咖啡因、肌醇、叶酸、泛酸和芳香类物质等多种化合物能调节脂肪代谢，特别是<a href="https://www.chaliyi.com/wulongcha/" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: blue; user-select: text !important;" target="_blank">乌龙茶</a>对蛋白质和脂肪有很好的分解作用。茶多酚和维生素c能降低胆固醇和血脂，所以饮碧螺春能减肥。</p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	<strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); user-select: text !important;">7、防龋齿作用</strong></p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;茶中含有氟，氟离子与牙齿的钙质有很大的亲和力，能变成一种较为难溶于酸的&ldquo;氟磷灰石&rdquo;，就像给牙齿加上一个保护层，提高了牙齿防酸抗龋能力。</p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	<strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); user-select: text !important;">8、抑制癌细胞作用</strong></p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	据报道，茶叶中的黄酮类物质有不同程度的体外抗癌作用。作用较强的有牡荆碱、桑色素和儿茶素。</p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	<strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); user-select: text !important;">9、缓解脚气作用</strong></p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	每晚睡前，取花椒10克、碧螺春10克、陈醋50毫升，加水2500毫升煮开，放温后浸泡双脚，每次浸泡半小时，然后用干净毛巾擦干双脚。坚持每晚泡脚1次，一般一周后脚气便会减轻。</p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	碧螺春的功效与作用还有有抗氧化、抗辐射、抗癌、降血糖、降血压、降血脂、抗菌、抗病毒、消臭等多种保健作用。</p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	<strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); user-select: text !important;">二、碧螺春的禁忌</strong></p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	1、不能饮用冷的碧螺春茶。冷茶对身体则有滞寒、聚痰的副作用。<br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; user-select: text !important;" />\r\n	2、不能空腹饮用碧螺春茶。空腹饮茶，茶性入肺腑，会冷脾胃。<br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; user-select: text !important;" />\r\n	3、碧螺春茶太烫不能饮用。太烫的茶对人的咽喉、食道和胃刺激较强。长期喝烫茶，可能引起这些器官病变。<br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; user-select: text !important;" />\r\n	4、不能饮用太浓的碧螺春茶。浓茶含咖啡因、茶碱多，刺激强，易引起头痛、失眠。<br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; user-select: text !important;" />\r\n	5、碧螺春茶不能冲泡时间太久。冲泡时间过长，茶叶中的茶多酚、芳香物质等可能自动氧化。<br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; user-select: text !important;" />\r\n	6、碧螺春茶汤不能搁置时间太久，会受到周围环境的污染，很不卫生。<br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; user-select: text !important;" />\r\n	7、碧螺春茶冲泡次数不能过多。一般茶叶在冲泡三四次后就没有什么儿茶素了，几乎没有保健作用了。<br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; user-select: text !important;" />\r\n	8、碧螺春茶不能饭前饮用。饭前饮茶会冲淡唾液，使饮食无味，还能暂时使消化器官吸收蛋白质的功能下降。<br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; user-select: text !important;" />\r\n	9、碧螺春茶不能饭后马上饮用。因为茶中含有鞣酸，能与食物中的蛋白质、铁质发生凝固作用，影响人体对蛋白质和铁质的消化吸收。<br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; user-select: text !important;" />\r\n	10、碧螺春茶不能和药物同时服用。茶叶中含有大量鞣质，可分解成鞣酸，与许多药物结合而产生沉淀，阻碍吸收，影响药效。<br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; user-select: text !important;" />\r\n	11、患有心血管疾病、消化道溃疡、肾功能不良的人不宜饮用碧螺春茶。<br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; user-select: text !important;" />\r\n	12、孕妇、儿童不宜多饮碧螺春茶。<br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; user-select: text !important;" />\r\n	13、寒性体质不宜饮用碧螺春。因为碧螺是未经发酵的茶，性质寒凉，且富含多酚类成分，寒性体质的人群饮用会雪上加霜，导致人出现精神虚弱，手脚冰冷、腹泻等症状。<br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; user-select: text !important;" />\r\n	14、胃病患者禁止饮用碧螺春茶。因茶多酚含量极高，对胃部有极强的收敛性和刺激性，胃病患者饮用，会加重病症。</p>\r\n', '', '', '0.0.0.0'),
