(70, 4, '<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	<img alt="银骏眉是什么茶银骏眉有什么功效" src="/qxcy/uploads/allimg/211027/163921J43-0.jpg" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px 15px; border: 0px; max-width: 790px; user-select: text !important;" /></p>\r\n<h3 style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); user-select: text !important;">\r\n	银骏眉</h3>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	骏眉是一种顶级<a href="https://www.chaliyi.com/zhengshanxiaozhong/" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: blue; user-select: text !important;" target="_blank">正山小种</a><a href="https://www.chaliyi.com/hongcha/" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: blue; user-select: text !important;" target="_blank">红茶</a>，首创于2005年。 根据<a href="https://www.chaliyi.com/" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: blue; user-select: text !important;" target="_blank">茶叶</a>的品质及采摘的标准不同，分为金骏眉、银骏眉。</p>\r\n<h3 style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); user-select: text !important;">\r\n	银骏眉知识介绍</h3>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	银骏眉是于谷雨前采摘于武夷山国家级自然保护区内海拔1500-1800米高山的原生态小种野茶的茶芽，制作500克银骏眉需数万颗标准嫩芽，一芽一叶。银骏眉在外形上条索紧细，锋苗显秀，稍显黄毫之色。</p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	银骏眉精心选取一芽一叶，以正山小种传统手工工艺进行制作，不过筛，所以条形保持完好，外形上已经类似于工夫红茶的条索了。银骏眉盖碗边的汤色显得绿黄清澈，汤色金黄清澈;银骏眉香气独特，清高持久，是一种花香与果香混合的综合香型，滋味鲜爽甘活，喉韵悠长。金骏眉、银骏眉一经投放市场，便引来茶友的追捧，一时间，正山小种市场掀起了金骏眉、银骏眉潮流。</p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	特点　　银骏眉外形：一芽一叶，紧结，均整，银灰色为上，金黄带红为次。</p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	香气：清爽，如蜜糖。</p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	汤色：橙黄、清澈、明亮为上;红、浊、暗为次。</p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	滋味：清爽、醇厚、甘甜，耐久泡。</p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	叶底：明亮，古铜色为上，红褐色为次。</p>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	银骏眉：武夷山红茶正山小种的特级红茶!</p>\r\n', '', '', '0.0.0.0'),
(71, 4, '<a href="https://www.chaliyi.com/hongcha/" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: blue; font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;" target="_blank">红茶</a><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; font-size: 16px;">里&ldquo;</span><a href="https://www.chaliyi.com/jinjunmei/" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: blue; font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;" target="_blank">金骏眉</a><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; font-size: 16px;">&rdquo;、&ldquo;</span><a href="https://www.chaliyi.com/zhengshanxiaozhong/" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: blue; font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;" target="_blank">正山小种</a><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; font-size: 16px;">&rdquo;名声叫得响亮，再怎么不懂红茶的人可能也略有耳闻，但&ldquo;赤甘&rdquo;之名却鲜少有人提起。</span><br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;" />\r\n<br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;" />\r\n<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; font-size: 16px;">所谓&ldquo;赤甘&rdquo;，赤者，红也；甘者，甜也，故名赤甘。&ldquo;赤甘&rdquo;系属红茶类，分为大赤甘和小赤甘，&ldquo;赤甘&rdquo;还有一个名称叫&ldquo;铜骏眉&rdquo;。</span>\r\n<p style="padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;">\r\n	<img alt="大小赤甘（铜骏眉）茶道的茶艺九步以及茶艺表演" src="/qxcy/uploads/allimg/211027/1641444G7-0.jpg" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px 15px; border: 0px; max-width: 790px; user-select: text !important;" /></p>\r\n<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; font-size: 16px;">第一道：布具&mdash;&mdash;将茶盘中的各个器具按一定的顺序摆放好。为了让嘉宾能更好地看到红茶的汤色，我们选用玻璃公道杯。</span><br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;" />\r\n<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; font-size: 16px;">第二道：赏茶&mdash;&mdash;</span><a href="https://www.chaliyi.com/" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: blue; font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;" target="_blank">茶叶</a><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; font-size: 16px;">在冲泡之前应先取出一小部分放入茶盘中，供客人鉴赏，这样一是表达诚意，二是使客人了解此茶的品质。</span><br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;" />\r\n<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; font-size: 16px;">第三道：涤器&mdash;&mdash;涤器是泡茶的重要环节，通过涤器可以高温消毒，又可给盖碗升温有利于茶汁的快速渗出，同时也显示洁净，体现对客人的尊敬。</span><br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;" />\r\n<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; font-size: 16px;">第四道：置茶&mdash;&mdash;&ldquo;置茶&rdquo;又称&ldquo;香茗入宫&rdquo;。根据客人的多少及壶的大小来确定投茶量。</span><br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;" />\r\n<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; font-size: 16px;">第五道：冲泡&mdash;&mdash;冲泡水温以85℃&mdash;90℃为宜。&ldquo;大小赤甘&rdquo;红茶冲泡时较适合缓冲</span><br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;" />\r\n<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; font-size: 16px;">第六道：温杯&mdash;&mdash;第一泡茶汤倒出之前所做的工作是温杯。这是迎接第一泡所做的工作之一，这样可使倒出的茶汤保持较高的热度，香气也能较好地发挥出来。</span><br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;" />\r\n<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; font-size: 16px;">第七道：分汤&mdash;&mdash;将盖碗中的茶汤倒入公道杯中，再将公道杯取出，沾贴于干燥的毛巾上除去壶上水分，把茶汤依次均匀地斟到每个茶杯中，使茶汤保持浓淡均匀。每个茶杯的茶汤达到七分满，留三分装我们的情意。</span><br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;" />\r\n<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; font-size: 16px;">第八道：闻香&mdash;&mdash;&ldquo;大小赤甘&rdquo;红茶的桂圆香、清甜香持久，仔细地闻一闻，感受这特殊的香味。</span><br style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; user-select: text !important;" />\r\n<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, SimSun; font-size: 16px;">第九道：品茗</span>', '', '', '0.0.0.0');
